==Mission==
Amizade empowers individuals and communities through worldwide service and learning.

==Vision==
Amizade imagines a world in which all people have the opportunity to explore and grow, realize their ability to make change, and embrace their responsibility to build a better world.
Our foundation is built on
* Cooperation and partnership across all boundaries
* Building global citizens
* Commitment to communities and their rights to fulfill their own goals
* Meeting basic human needs
* Challenging assumptions and growing through intercultural exchange
